Quiver

Graph Neural Network Operators for heterogeneous hardware.

Quick Run Benchmark

```
./U # upgrade quiver installation

./benchmarks/ogbn_products_sage/run.sh
./benchmarks/cora/run.sh
```

Code Structure

*.cu.hpp // cuda template
*.hpp // c++ header or template
*.cu  // cuda kernels
*.cpp // c++ implementations


Develop

- run ./scripts/lint.sh to format python code before push

### Generate docs

    pip install mkdocs-material
    pip install mkdocstrings
    mkdocs serve

